text.tspan: I enjoy expressing creativity, solving problems, facing
challenges and focusing on results. I have over 8 years of
experience in team driven environments. My passion for
solving problems using technology, along with my extensive
background as a team leader has enabled me to make unique
and valuable contributions to group projects that you will
observe here. When I am not building software you can find
me hanging with my family, painting or writing music.
